name: Celia Aintree(Walkure Romance)|スィーリア|蘇利亞|苏利亚|少女騎士物語
description:
This is a character from the GAL game “Walkure Romance”! Thank you all for reviews and feedback!

Please use the following trigger prompt:

celia\(walkure\): character

celia\(armor\): wear armor

celia\(uniform\): wear uniform

Recommended Lora model strength selection 0.6~0.8

Recommended base model: Meinamix( https://civitai.com/models/7240/meinamix)

For example, this prompt can generate photos of Celia wearing armor:

celia\(walkure\), celia\(armor\), 1girl, solo, mature female,

best quality, highest quality, ultra-detailed, masterpiece, illustration:1,

<lora:celia_walkure:0.6>

And this prompt could generate a picture of Celia in uniform:

celia\(walkure\), celia\(uniform\), 1girl, solo, mature female,

best quality, highest quality, ultra-detailed, masterpiece, illustration:1,

<lora:celia_walkure:0.6>

Please do not use it for any commercial purpose.

If there is any infringement, please contact me to delete it, thank you.

--

触发词 prompt:

celia\(walkure\), 人物角色

celia\(armor\): 铠甲

celia\(uniform\): 制服

Lora 模型强度推荐选择 0.6~0.8

Base model 推荐选择 Meinamix( https://civitai.com/models/7240/meinamix)

例如这样可以生成穿铠甲的照片

celia\(walkure\), celia\(armor\), 1girl, solo, mature female,

best quality, highest quality, ultra-detailed, masterpiece, illustration:1,

<lora:celia_walkure:0.6>

这样可以生成穿制服的图片：

celia\(walkure\), celia\(uniform\), 1girl, solo, mature female,

best quality, highest quality, ultra-detailed, masterpiece, illustration:1,

<lora:celia_walkure:0.6>

請勿用於任何商業用途!

如有版权方认为侵权，请联系我删除，谢谢!

--

感谢原作者こもりけい老师，感谢秋叶大佬提供Lora训练整合包和教程，感谢AI算法大神们的研究成果！

世界上喜欢Celia的人还蛮多的吼。单靠我一个人，我的显卡就是累死，也满足不了那么多爱看涩图的绅士。

经过反复认真思考，我做了一个违背祖宗的决定，把这个秘方无偿的贡献给国家，让大家批量生产，自给自足，就像种韭菜一样。

但是我劝，各位年轻的小同志，少玩电脑，多交女友，多搞窝里斗。最后祝你，身体健康，谢谢朋友们！
